show.description: A victorious king returns to a hero’s welcome, only to find his kingdom threatened by dark conspiracies targeting his loved ones. As ruthless forces close in on his beloved Feier, he must confront merciless enemies willing to kill for power. Bound by love and vengeance, he races against time to protect his legacy and bring justice to those who betrayed him.
